Title: Superstar
Writer: Xavier Giannoli, Serge Joncour (novel), Marcia Romano (collaboration)
Actors: Kad Merad, Cécile de France, Louis-Do de Lencquesaing, Cédric Ben Abdallah
Plot: An average guy who works in a recycling plant wakes up one morning to discover that he's become inexplicably famous.
